metadata.name: Flower-Venus Byzantium
metadata.description:
Sexuality and Desire are breaking by the Other Law, being in the co-joined fall into the abyss between Epochs. Who’s hysterical here? — A woman that is both unable to cherish and hold in her embrace that falling into abyss Other? — or Other that makes the epoch fall down and the Woman’s world break into pieces?

Venus turns into a beautiful and tender water lily, if you help her open up, protect her from falling.  But it will become predatory and dangerous if you let it fall and break.

Outside The Box lab created an accompanying piece of music inspired by the Greek, with an emphasis on motifs popular in epic cinema, blackness refers to the complexity and mystery of all the vicissitudes of myths and culture.

Music: 
Outside The Box lab (Victor Eremenko, Gleb Ostrovskiy)

June 2022
